OL,5, The BBC's director general Tim Davie   
OL,6, has announced that the corporation will
OL,7, explore licence fee reform.            
OL,9,FIn a speech on Tuesday, Davie said "it 
OL,10,Fis right to ask fundamental questions  
OL,11,Fabout its longevity".                  
OL,13,FBut he also criticised cuts to the BBC 
OL,14,Fin real terms in recent years.         
OL,16,F"To strip money from the BBC during    
OL,17,Fthis period has been particularly      
OL,18,Fshort-sighted" after "below            
OL,19,Finflationary settlements have chipped  
OL,20,Faway at our income over many years."   
